description: Demolition of existing building and erection a  part two storey, rising to part eight storey building with retail use (Class A1) at ground floor and 75 residential units (Class C3) on the upper floors, in a mix of one, two and three bedroomed self contained flats ( 7 affordable units). Provision of associated landscaping, 75 cycle spaces, 7 motorbike spaces, 20 shared parking spaces for the commercial and residential uses and 62 basement car parking spaces for residential use, accessed from Church Hill Road.
